# The area of interest
0 2000 10       # Model extension and the number of cells in x direction
0 2000 10       # Model extension and the number of cells in x direction
0 1000 5        # Model extension and the number of cells in z direction

# Padding parameters. The sizes of padding cells is increased towards the boundary.
0          # Number of padding cells on +x and -x sides
0          # Increasing factor for the sizes of padding cells in x direction. 
0          # Number of padding cells on +y and -y sides
0          # Increasing factor for the sizes of padding cells in y direction
0          # Number of padding cells at bottom (on the +z side)
0          # Increasing factor for the sizes of padding cells in z direction
